      <p class="hero-english" data-hero>
        Short frame. Clear mind. Better sleep.
      </p>

      <a href="https://tally.so/r/RGYNNl" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-amber hero-cta" data-hero>申請入群</a>

